      "span_text": "Previous studies have produced conflicting results but suggest that ApoE 4 carriers may be more susceptible to lobar haemorrhagic strokes caused by cerebral amyloid angiopathy, but probably not hypertension-related haemorrhages [CITATION_1] ."
